name: pg-structure

scripts.doc: npm run doc:mkdocs && npm run doc:readme
scripts.doc:readme: jsdoc2md "lib/**/*" > JSDOC.md; cat docs/link-to-doc.md docs/index.md > README.md; rm -f JSDOC.md docs/link-to-doc.md;
scripts.postversion: npm run doc && git add -A site && git add README.md mkdocs.yml && git commit -m 'Doc update.' && git push && git push --tags && git subtree push --prefix site origin gh-pages && npm publish;
